import './ProfileCard.css' export const ProfileCard = ({profile}) => { console.log(profile) const {_id, Category, Name, Address, City, State, PinCode, ContactNumber, ContactMail, Course} = profile; let subject = " "; for (const key of Object.keys(Course)) { if (Array.isArray(Course[key])) { subject += key + ": " + Course[key].join(', '); } } return (

{Name}

{subject}

{Address}, {City}, {State}, {PinCode}

Ready to teach: {Category}

Contact Details

{ContactNumber}

{ContactMail}

star 4.3
) }
